OL,4,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,5,C"I DON'T HALF MISS A FRY-UP!"          
OL,7, Everytime a devout veggie mate of mine 
OL,8, passes a greasy-spoon cafe, she has to 
OL,9, hold her breath - the scent of sizzling
OL,10, sausages and crackling bacon isCtoo    
OL,11,Cmuch of a temptation,Gshe reasons.     
OL,13, I, like thousands of veggies and vegans
OL,14, world-over, can empathise with her     
OL,15, feelings, but there'sCno need to go    
OL,16,Cwithout,Gthere are meat-free versions! 
OL,18, The Green SceneCputs some to the test  
OL,19, and rustles up a few tasty recipes...  
OL,20,B``````````````````````````````````1/8``
