OL,5,C"I DON'T HALF MISS A FRY-UP!"          
OL,7,CThe Redwood Company,Gproduces a wide   
OL,8, range of soya-based bacon rashers,     
OL,9, suitable for vegetarians and vegans.   
OL,10, We tried:                              
OL,12,CCheatin' rashersG(#1.99 for 8 slices): 
OL,13, "Pop these under the grill and judging 
OL,14, by the aroma, you wouldn't know they   
OL,15, aren't the real thing. To taste, they  
OL,16, reminded me of smokey bacon crisps."   
OL,18,BGFor details of your nearest          
OL,19, stockists, callC01536 400 557.         
