OL,5,C"I DON'T HALF MISS A FRY-UP!"          
OL,7,CWicken FenGproduces a range of gourmet 
OL,8,Gvegetarian sausages which contain no   
OL,9,Gartificial colourings, flavourings or  
OL,10,Gpreservatives. Our favourite was the:  
OL,11,G                                       
OL,12,CMexicanaG(#1.60 for 6): "With a strong 
OL,13,Gspicy bean flavour, these are very     
OL,14,Gasty. Would be ideal served with mashed
OL,15,Gpotatoes and gravy."                   
OL,16,G                                       
OL,17,BGAvailable fromCTescoGandCAsdaGstores,
OL,18,Gbut for details of local stockists or  
OL,19,Gto mail order, callC01361 883150.      
