OL,5,C"I DON'T HALF MISS A FRY-UP!"          
OL,7,CHolland & BarrettGhave created meat-   
OL,8, free sausages which do not contain any 
OL,9, artificial colourings or preservatives.
OL,10, What's more they're suitable for vegans
OL,11, and vegetarians alike:                 
OL,13,BCChilled SausagesG(Pack of 6 for 99p):
OL,14, "Though plain to taste, they had a nice
OL,15, chunky texture and grilled very well.  
OL,16, Best smothered in tomato sauce."       
