OL,4,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,5,CVEGGIE BACON'N'BANANA SARNIES          
OL,6,CIngredients:                           
OL,7,R$G2 slices bread                       
OL,8,R$GButter or vegan margarine to spread  
OL,9,R$G\ one medium banana, sliced          
OL,10,R$G30ml/2tbsps vegan mayonnaise         
OL,11,R$G5ml/1tsp vegetable oil               
OL,12,R$G3 slices Redwood Company's rashers   
OL,13,R$G2 lettuce leaves                     
OL,14,CMethod:                                
OL,15,BGSpread the bread with the butter or  
OL,16, marge. Toss the banana in mayonnaise,  
OL,17, season. Heat oil in a pan and lightly  
OL,18, fry the rashers. Fill sarnie with      
OL,19, rashers, lettuce and banana. Mmmmm.... 
