OL,4,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,5,CBARBECUED WICKEN FEN KEBABSG(Serves 6) 
OL,6,CIngredients:                           
OL,7,R$G1 packet Wicken Fen sausages         
OL,8,R$G3 onions, quartered                  
OL,9,R$G6 tomatoes, quartered                
OL,10,R$G3 red or green peppers, cubed        
OL,11,R$GKebab sticks                         
OL,12,R$GOlive oil                            
OL,13,CMethod:                                
OL,14,BGCut the sausages into one inch       
OL,15, pieces and thread on the kebab sticks: 
OL,16, pepper, sausage, onion, sausage,       
OL,17, tomato, sausage, pepper.               
OL,18,BGPlace on barbecue, drizzle with olive
OL,19, oil, turning for 3-4 mins until cooked.
OL,20,B``````````````````````````````````6/8``
