OL,3,R j}j}j} ~5j5~5 ~5 j5j5U #k
OL,4,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,5,CTOAD IN THE HOLEG(Serves 4)            
OL,6,CIngredients:                           
OL,7,R$G1 packet Wicken Fen sausages         
OL,8, (suggested flavour - Tomato & Garlic)  
OL,9,R$G4oz plain flour                      
OL,10,R$G\ pint milk                          
OL,11,R$G2 eggs                               
OL,12,R$GVegetable oil                        
OL,13,R$GSalt and pepper                      
OL,14,CMethod:                                
OL,16,BGPreheat the oven to gas mark 7, 425F 
OL,17, or 220C. To make batter, sift flour,   
OL,18, work in eggs, add milk, whisk.         
OL,19,                             C Contd >>>
OL,20,B``````````````````````````````````7/8``
