OL,4,B```````````````````````````````````````
OL,5,CTOAD IN THE HOLEG(Serves 4)            
OL,6,CMethod:G(Continued...)                 
OL,8,BGHeat 1 tblsp of oil in a roasting    
OL,9, dish. Add a quarter of the batter to   
OL,10, the hot oil, run it around the         
OL,11, roasting dish.                         
OL,13,BGPlace the uncooked sausages in the   
OL,14, roasting dish and pour over the        
OL,15, remaining batter.                      
OL,17,BGCook until the batter is crisped     
OL,18, and puffed up.                         
OL,20,B``````````````````````````````````8/8``
